widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At Aatulya Wellness, we strive to provide a seamless and enriching experience for all our participants. Our <strong>Refund and Cancellation Policy<\/strong> is designed to be transparent, fair, and consistent, ensuring clarity for our valued customers.<\/p><h3>1. Conditions for Refunds<\/h3><p>Refunds are available under specific circumstances, including:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Event Cancellation:<\/strong> If we cancel a workshop, retreat, or event, a full refund will be issued.<\/li><li><strong>Significant Changes:<\/strong> If there are substantial changes to the event details (e.g., date, time, location, or instructor), you may be eligible for a refund.<\/li><li><strong>Non-Delivery of Services:<\/strong> If we fail to provide the services promised at the time of booking, you may request a refund.<\/li><\/ul><p>Refunds will not be issued for personal reasons, such as a change of mind, scheduling conflicts, or failure to attend an event.<\/p><h3>2. Non-Refundable Fees<\/h3><p>Certain fees may be non-refundable. These will be communicated during the booking process, such as:<\/p><ul><li>Processing or administrative fees<\/li><li>Any other fees explicitly stated as non-refundable at the time of booking<\/li><\/ul><h3>3. Refund Process<\/h3><p>To request a refund, please reach out to us within the specified time frame after your booking. The process is as follows:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Contact Us:<\/strong> Email your refund request to <strong>aatulyayoga@gmail.com<\/strong>, providing your booking details and the reason for your request.<\/li><li><strong>Eligibility Check:<\/strong> We will verify your eligibility for a refund based on the terms of this policy.<\/li><li><strong>Refund Issuance:<\/strong> Approved refunds will be processed within the specified time frame. Refunds will be credited to the original payment method used during booking.<\/li><\/ul><p>Please allow some time for the refund to reflect in your account, depending on the payment method used.<\/p><h3>4. Proof of Purchase<\/h3><p>To process a refund, we may require proof of your purchase, such as a booking confirmation or receipt. Please keep a record of your booking details for reference.<\/p><h3>5. Cancellation Policy<\/h3><p>You can cancel your booking within a specified time frame prior to the event date. Please note the following:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Cancellation Window:<\/strong> Cancellations made before the specified deadline will be eligible for a refund (subject to the conditions of this policy).<\/li><li><strong>Late Cancellations:<\/strong> Requests made after this period may not be accepted, and no refund will be issued.<\/li><\/ul><p>To cancel your booking, please contact our support team at <strong>aatulyayoga@gmail.com.<\/strong><\/p><h3>6. Partial Cancellations<\/h3><p>In cases where partial cancellations are allowed (e.g., cancelling a portion of a multi-day retreat), the refund will be prorated based on the unused portion of the service.<\/p><h3>7. Non-Transferable Bookings<\/h3><p>Please note that all bookings are non-transferable. If you need to make changes to the attendee details, please contact us, and we will review your request. Changes are subject to approval and may incur additional fees.<\/p><h3>8. Attendee Substitutions<\/h3><p>If you are unable to attend an event, you may request a substitution for another person. Substitutions are allowed only with prior approval from our team, and any applicable fees may apply.<\/p><h3>9. Contact Us<\/h3><p>For any questions or assistance with cancellations or refunds, please contact us at:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Email:<\/strong> aatulyayoga@gmail.com<\/li><li><strong>Phone:<\/strong> +91 72898 79684<\/li><li><strong>Address:<\/strong> 2p-20 Talwandi, Kota, Rajasthan 324005, India<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\